sailpoint.object
Interface LinkInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
Link, LinkSnapshot, NativeChangeDetection
public interface LinkInterface

An read-only interface for Links (for example - application accounts). This provides a common interface to Links and LinkSnapshots.
